Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 烟花大会要不要穿浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不穿 穿起来太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 穿浴衣的确行动不便
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木屐还伤脚 不穿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 还是行动方便好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是暑假第一个能见到马渕的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修子的上衣好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也该选件可爱点的...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.40,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双叶 修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 悠里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位都好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠里...你今天穿浴衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天的女生会上不是说好不穿了吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没说不穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确没说...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过感觉就你一人穿好狡猾...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双叶不也是吗 偷偷冲到马渕家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷调查他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也得...我也得加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 找到啦找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村尾 好久不见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槙田穿的浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 挺好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天还卷了下头发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很配你 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉今天的悠里 刚开场就放大招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明她跟你一样不愿输
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不甘心 你就只有加油了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力...这...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都下决心要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个 那边那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 村尾 打靶哦打靶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村尾 你想要哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 来一回的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对会打给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马渕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃不吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 小兄弟安慰奖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 来一回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中大奖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抹茶红豆刨冰的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马渕的是什么味的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情侣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃刨冰吗 修子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换着吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像情侣似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你不喜欢换着吃来着 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不枉我穿浴衣来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠里危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠里没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 马渕扶住我了 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花几点开始放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7点 快了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马渕看上去也很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要够努力 我也可以比双叶更近一步的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要比双叶近...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你们去前面等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我想跟你聊一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去那边聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马渕很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥...把那件事忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是场小误会 或者说是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 不是说忘就忘的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了那种事...我还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是我想忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干了那种事又单方面说要忘掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...洸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事...吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到现场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊 你太差劲了 痴女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洸 你误会啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥叫那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋 丢死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦不烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不知该说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要聊到啥时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是怕男生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买点吃的来 谁要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要炒面加烤肠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了吉冈那份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 悠里和洸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？两人一起去的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经拜托他们买吉冈那份了 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马渕 看上去心情不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为双叶刚才跟那人说话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拼命缩短的距离 根本算不上什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算穿这浴衣...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被木屐带勒到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能等我贴下创可贴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:08:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带创可贴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我总是随身带着的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凑打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算说我是女生...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可马渕不喜欢有什么意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之槙田受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 马上就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槙田 怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贴好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰带有点紧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿来 我来给你贴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 都怪我要穿浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣不就是这时候穿的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比穿着短裤来看烟花的人要好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马渕果然...喜欢双叶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么努力 连浴衣都穿上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还换了个可爱点的发型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 什么都不做的双叶...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槙田 怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 很疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去找医务室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论我怎么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许都是徒劳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槙田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 要是一直不说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚肯定会因为嫉妒双叶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在变成那样之前...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马渕 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁自己还没变讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:11:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢马渕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 不过我对槙田从未有过这方面的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马渕难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让我过下 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠里 悠里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠里 伤到哪了 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫了我那么多次 直卯卯地朝我赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:12:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着她这样 感觉已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双叶 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天回家之后哭个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后 虽然悠里和洸仍然聊了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过悠里已经不再占着洸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好悠里只是被木屐带勒到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你只说了句她受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时可急死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是受伤了啊 我又没说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说你说明不足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为悠里跟他说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过洸看上去还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠里还没告白吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换做是我 能说出口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这两个字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能说出口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出喜欢这两个字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（喜欢）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 还没完 真长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没发现 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？你说啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你后面有人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心点 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我们没去成的夏日祭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我不知洸对我说的算不算约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直后悔为何没好好确认下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7点 三角公园的时钟下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 就这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洸就只说了这句 太难懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7点 三角公园的时钟下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难懂了 真赖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才那是重新跟你约定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那天悠里和修子都要跟家人出门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得小凑也...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是两个人去？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去 我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就该这么说 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想现在就喊出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人一起去祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要穿浴衣呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天都没穿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要穿怕是跟关取似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这太过分了 快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼...别用前腿踢我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前腿？你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉洸的笑容跟之前有些不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看见这种笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪还气得起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣 穿浴衣来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不明摆着的吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再待会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我貌似说了句不得了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得...不太尽兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给男人留空子的后果可是很严重的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:18:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...洸你什么都不会做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许正因为是洸我才不怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 真心不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你送到家吧 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了连自己都无法相信的大胆的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为夏天的夜晚在作怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你送我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你刚才在铁道口到底说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先留着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 夏日祭见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉 就像摸索着互相靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后只差1毫米的语言和态度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟令人如此心动 舒心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 把浴衣拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在夏日祭那天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上浴衣 再换个可爱的发型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲口对洸说喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 夏日祭去不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出啥事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等悠里来了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双叶 修 想死你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的暑假就在这样的气氛中慢慢结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要一步步 一步步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细细品味 细细体会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天我请你们吃甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修子 修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 云貌似散了点

